headline: Techcon Launches New Side-By-Side Dispensing Cartridge Line
summary: Techcon, part of OK International and Dover (NYSE: DOV) and a leader in precision fluid dispensing technologies, today announced the launch of its new line of Side-by-Side (SBS) Dispensing Cartridges for the electronics, industrial, medical device and automotive industries.

headline: Mizuho Boosts Dover (DOV) Price Target Citing Lower Tariff Risk and Strategic Investments
summary: Dover Corporation (NYSE:DOV) ranks among the top stocks for an early retirement portfolio. Mizuho maintained its Outperform rating on Dover Corporation (NYSE:DOV) while increasing its price target from $215 to $225 on June 13. The research firm’s more optimistic view was attributed in large part to “accelerating secular trends” and a “derisked 2025 guide” in […]
